#!/bin/bash
echo "---- Install deps"
sudo add-apt-repository multiverse
sudo dpkg --add-architecture i386
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y lib32gcc1 libsdl2-2.0-0:i386 docker.io awscli unzip
TOKEN=$(curl -SsfX PUT "http://169.254.169.254/latest/api/token" -H "X-aws-ec2-metadata-token-ttl-seconds: 21600")
INSTANCE_ID=$(curl -SsfH "X-aws-ec2-metadata-token: $TOKEN" http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/instance-id)
aws --region us-east-2 ec2 attach-volume --volume-id

--instance-id $INSTANCE_ID --device /dev/xvdf
while ! test -e /dev/xvdf; do sleep 1; done
mkfs -t xfs /dev/xvdf
mkdir /mnt/sheeta
mount /dev/xvdf /mnt/sheeta
echo "UUID=$(lsblk -o +UUID | grep thepain | awk '{print $8}') /mnt/sheeta  xfs  defaults,nofail  0  2" >> /etc/fstab
echo "---- Add users"
sudo usermod -aG docker ubuntu
sudo usermod -aG docker steam
echo "---- Install PZ"
mkdir /mnt/sheeta
docker run -v /mnt/sheeta:/data steamcmd/steamcmd:ubuntu-18         +login anonymous         +force_install_dir /data         +app_update 380870 validate         +quit
mkdir -p $(dirname '/mnt/sheeta/files/')
aws s3 cp 's3://cdk-hnb659fds-assets-208744038881-us-east-2/9cf8071398f381ec20504a3e2efb9bd5060f49d4278a8f32430112ea2e3fc534.zip' '/mnt/sheeta/files/'
mkdir -p $(dirname '/mnt/sheeta/files/')
aws s3 cp 's3://cdk-hnb659fds-assets-208744038881-us-east-2/a3e1442c916b889a1057967a4e3b63041869c933e8548e9a6ae680d6c8bb2ae4.zip' '/mnt/sheeta/files/'
mkdir -p /mnt/sheeta/Server/
unzip /mnt/sheeta/files/9cf8071398f381ec20504a3e2efb9bd5060f49d4278a8f32430112ea2e3fc534.zip -d /mnt/sheeta/Server/
unzip /mnt/sheeta/files/a3e1442c916b889a1057967a4e3b63041869c933e8548e9a6ae680d6c8bb2ae4.zip -d /etc/systemd/system/
chmod +x /etc/systemd/system/sheeta.service
systemctl enable sheeta_service.service
systemctl start sheeta_service.service
